## Workflow Overview

The `lrda_mobile` repository contains a single GitHub Actions workflow located under `.github/workflows/Native.yml`.

This workflow provides a basic continuous integration pipeline that executes automated testing when code changes occur.

Current automation includes:

- Triggering on `push` and `pull_request` events to the `main` branch
- Repository checkout
- Node.js runtime setup
- Dependency installation via Yarn
- Automated test execution

The workflow validates application behavior through testing but does not currently include advanced CI/CD capabilities such as caching, deployment, security scanning, or artifact generation.

